olylineFeature":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolylineFeature","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNPolylineFeature","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolylinefeature","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolylineFeature","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolylineFeature","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object associates a polyline shape with an optional"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"identifier and attributes."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShape"}],"abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is an abstract class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the content that forms the base map."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","title":"MLNShape"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPoint":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint"},{"type":"text","text":" class is an abstract superclass used to define shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"composed of multiple vertices."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPoint"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","