hen serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNFeature":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNFeature"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnfeature","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature"},{"text":"  protocol is used to provide details about geographic features","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"contained in an ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource"},{"text":" object. Each concrete","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"text":" in turn has a subclass that conforms to this protocol. A","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"feature object associates a shape with an optional identifier and attributes.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNFeature","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","role":"symbol"}}}